OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable' bullying at
OL,4,Chospitals uncovered by inspectors
OL,6,FHospital inspectors have found that
OL,7,Fbullying, racism, sexism and a knock-
OL,8,Fon impact on patient care are still
OL,9,Fongoing at Birmingham's main hospitals
OL,10,Ftrust - within the trust.
OL,12,FUniversity Hospitals Birmingham NHS
OL,13,FTrust, which runs the Queen Elizabeth,
OL,14,FHeartlands, Good Hope and Solihull
OL,15,Fhospitals, has been downgraded to a
OL,16,F'requires improvement' overall rating,
OL,17,Ffollowing an inspection by health
OL,18,Fwatchdog, the Care Quality Commission.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/14
