OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable' bullying at
OL,4,Chospitals uncovered by inspectors
OL,6,FInspectors said the trust is still
OL,7,Ffailing many of their staff, despite a
OL,8,Frestructure, change in leadership and
OL,9,Fnew initiatives - with its 'well led'
OL,10,Frating being downgraded to
OL,11,F'inadequate'.
OL,13,FThe report revealed some staff don't
OL,14,Ffeel safe from bullying or harassment,
OL,15,Fwhich undoes much of the excellent,
OL,16,Finnovative work and compassion and
OL,17,Fcare provided, according to the CQC.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
