OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable' bullying at
OL,4,Chospitals uncovered by inspectors
OL,6,FThe report stated that although there
OL,7,Fwere "genuine efforts to learn and
OL,8,Fimprove", there were still a "worrying
OL,9,Fnumber of staff across the
OL,10,Forganisation who felt the trust didn't
OL,11,Fhave an open culture where they could
OL,12,Fraise concerns without fear of blame
OL,13,For punishment. Also, some staff didn't
OL,14,Ffeel safe and protected from bullying
OL,15,Fand harassment, which had a negative
OL,16,Feffect on their wellbeing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/14
