OL,3,C'Completely unacceptable' bullying at
OL,4,Chospitals uncovered by inspectors
OL,6,FIt added: "This is completely
OL,7,Funacceptable and must be addressed by
OL,8,Fleaders as a priority to enable staff
OL,9,Fto feel supported and be able to
OL,10,Fprovide the best possible care to
OL,11,Fpeople."
OL,13,FInspectors also ruled the quality of
OL,14,Fcritical care for patients had
OL,15,Fdeteriorated badly, and emergency
OL,16,Fdepartments at the three main
OL,17,Fhospitals were deemed 'inadequate' on
OL,18,Fsafety measures.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/14
