OL,4,Chospitals uncovered by inspectors
OL,6,FNeurological services at the QE and
OL,7,Fmedical care at Good Hope were also
OL,8,Frated 'inadequate', and maternity
OL,9,Fservices at Heartlands had not
OL,10,Fimproved since a warning notice was
OL,11,Fissued earlier last year and remain
OL,12,F'inadequate'.
OL,14,FCancer services at the QE 'require
OL,15,Fimprovement' while critical care
OL,16,Fservices were downgraded to 'require
OL,17,Fimprovement'. Inspectors visited in
OL,18,FAugust and October last year to check
OL,19,Fout the trust's progress in a range of
OL,20,Fareas in the wake of damaging previous
OL,21,Ffindings.
