OL,6,FThe key findings across the trust were:
OL,8,FAlongside positive observations on
OL,9,Fimprovements at the trust:
OL,11,FIn a statement, Dame Yve Buckland,
OL,12,FChair, and Jonathan Brotherton, Chief
OL,13,FExecutive, at University Hospitals
OL,14,FBirmingham said:
OL,16,F"We are pleased that the CQC's
OL,17,Ffindings recognise that while
OL,18,Fimprovement is still in its early
OL,19,Fstages, with good initial work done,
OL,20,Fthe significant change required will
OL,21,Ftake time.
