OL,6,F"We believe that the significant
OL,7,Fchanges in our leadership, the new
OL,8,Fdevolved group operating model with
OL,9,Flocal hospital-based leadership and
OL,10,Fthe actions set out in our improvement
OL,11,Fprogramme, since the CQC's visit,
OL,12,Fevidence our commitment to learning,
OL,13,Fimproving and evolving.
OL,15,F"But we know that culture change
OL,16,Fcannot be fixed rapidly, or
OL,17,Fsuperficially, and that we have a
OL,18,Fconsiderable amount of work to do so
OL,19,Fthat the changes are felt by all
OL,20,Fcolleagues.
