OL,6,F"We are disappointed in the rating
OL,7,Fchange for our critical care services
OL,8,Fat the Queen Elizabeth Hospital
OL,9,FBirmingham. Since the CQC's
OL,10,Finspection, there have been
OL,11,Fsignificant improvements with
OL,12,Frecruitment and retention, within a
OL,13,Fdepartment made fragile and deeply
OL,14,Fimpacted by being on the front line of
OL,15,Fthe COVID-19 pandemic, with now a near-
OL,16,Ffull establishment of staff and an
OL,17,Fimproving skill mix.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
